ATNM finally after numerous back and forth emails with Steve he finally acknowledged that the status of the health canada clincal trial was incorrect and promised me that it will be fixed ASAP Trial status has now been updated from Pending to ongoingDefinitions of status are mentioned belowTrial Status PENDING status means Health Canada is pending the receipt of information from the sponsor indicating that the trial started An ONGOING status means Health Canada has received information from the sponsor indicating the proposed study start date ENDED status means Health Canada has received information from the sponsor indicating that the clinical trial has ended
